Package: pollster
Type: Package
Title: Calculate Crosstab and Topline Tables of Weighted Survey Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: John D. Johnson
Maintainer: John D. Johnson <john.d.johnson@marquette.edu>
Description: Calculate weighted topline and crosstab tables of simple weighted survey data.
    Optionally, include the margin of error. Output takes the form of tibbles (simple data frames).
    This package conveniently handles labelled data, such as that commonly used by Stata and SPSS.
    Complex survey design is not supported at this time.
Imports:
   dplyr,
   stringr,
   tidyr,
   labelled,
   lubridate,
   forcats
Suggests:
	ggplot2,
	knitr
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
